text: Elathur State assembly constituency () is one of the 140 state legislative assembly constituencies in Kerala state in southern India. It is also one of the 7 state legislative assembly constituencies included in the Kozhikode Lok Sabha constituency. As of the 2016 assembly election, the current MLA is A. K.
